      ja: {"term":"内外読み書き分離","kana":"ドクショブンリ","note":"更新処理（Write）をマスターDBに集中させ、読み取り処理（Read）をレプリカDBに分散させてスケーラビリティを高める設計。"},
      zh: {"term":"读写分离","explanation":"将数据库的写操作发送给主库（Master），读操作分配给多个从库（Replica）以大幅度提升系统查询吞吐量的分治架构。"},
      en: {"term":"Read-Write Splitting","explanation":"A database scaling design where write operations are routed to a primary database instance and read queries are distributed across replicas."},
      my: {"term":"ဖတ်ရှုခြင်းနှင့် ရေးသားခြင်း ခွဲခြားခြင်းစနစ်","explanation":"ဒေတာပြင်ဆင်မှု (write) ကို master database ထံ ပို့ပြီး၊ ရှာဖွေဖတ်ရှုမှု (read) ကို replica database များထံ မျှဝေပေးသည့် စနစ်。","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Phân tách đọc viết","explanation":"Thiết kế kiến trúc cơ sở dữ liệu định tuyến các truy vấn ghi (write) tới máy chủ chính và truy vấn đọc (read) tới các bản sao (replica)。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Séparation lecture-écriture","explanation":"Technique d'architecture orientant les écritures vers un serveur maître et distribuant les lectures sur des réplicas。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["Read-Write Split"],
      related: [],
      example: {"text":"Read-write splitting protects the primary database server from being overwhelmed by reporting queries."},
