      zh: {"term":"著作权保护","explanation":"法律赋予文学、艺术、科学及计算机软件等作品创作者的专有权利保护，采用无须登记自动产生的无方式主义。"},
      en: {"term":"Copyright Protection","explanation":"A legal right that grants the creator of an original work exclusive rights for its use and distribution, typically for a limited time."},
