      ja: {"term":"製造物責任法 (PL法)","kana":"セイゾウブツセキニンホウ","note":"製造物の欠陥により消費者などが損害を被った場合、製造元の過失の有無に関わらず、欠陥の証明のみで損害賠償責任を負わせる法律。"},
      zh: {"term":"产品责任法","explanation":"消费者权益保护法律。若产品因缺陷导致用户人身或财产损害，制造商或销售商即使无主观过失也须承担赔偿责任（严格责任原则），简称 PL 法。"},
      en: {"term":"Product Liability Act","explanation":"A law holding manufacturers and distributors responsible for injury or damage caused by defects in their products, regardless of negligence."},
      my: {"term":"ထုတ်ကုန် တာဝန်ယူမှုဥပဒေ","explanation":"ထုတ်လုပ်ထားသော ပစ္စည်းတစ်ခု၏ ချို့ယွင်းချက်ကြောင့် သုံးစွဲသူထိခိုက်ပါက ထုတ်လုပ်သူတွင် အပြည့်အဝ တာဝန်ရှိကြောင်း ပြဋ္ဌာန်းသည့် ဥပဒေ (PL Law)。","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Luật trách nhiệm sản phẩm","explanation":"Đạo luật quy định nhà sản xuất phải bồi thường cho người tiêu dùng nếu sản phẩm bị lỗi gây thiệt hại mà không cần chứng minh lỗi vô ý。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Loi sur la responsabilité du fait des produits","explanation":"Loi (responsabilité du fait des produits défectueux) contraignant les fabricants à réparer les dommages causés par un défaut de leur produit。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["PL Act","Strict liability law"],
      related: [],
      example: {"text":"The Product Liability Act applies to software when it is embedded in physical hardware like cars."},
      source: "project-glossary-v2",
