      zh: {"term":"个人信息保护法","explanation":"旨在规范个人数据处理活动，保障个人隐私与数据安全，规定处理者合法使用义务与用户知情同意权的法律规范。"},
      en: {"term":"Act on the Protection of Personal Information","explanation":"A law designed to protect personal rights and interests while ensuring the proper handling and security of personal information."},
