      ja: {"term":"秘密保持契約 (NDA)","kana":"ヒミツホジケイヤク","note":"取引や交渉の過程で開示された営業秘密や技術情報を、第三者に漏洩したり目的外に使用したりすることを禁止する契約。"},
      zh: {"term":"保密协议","explanation":"两方或多方之间达成的法律契约。规定合作过程中彼此披露的商业秘密与核心技术信息不得向任何第三方泄漏，简称 NDA。"},
      en: {"term":"Non-Disclosure Agreement","explanation":"A legal contract between at least two parties that outlines confidential material, knowledge, or information that the parties wish to share with one another."},
      my: {"term":"လျှို့ဝှက်ချက်ထိန်းသိမ်းမှု သဘောတူစာချုပ်","explanation":"လုပ်ငန်းပူးပေါင်းဆောင်ရွက်စဉ် အချင်းချင်း ဖလှယ်သော လျှို့ဝှက်ချက်များကို ပြင်ပသို့ ပေါက်ကြားခြင်းမရှိစေရန် ချုပ်ဆိုသည့် စာချုပ် (NDA)。","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Thỏa thuận bảo mật thông tin","explanation":"Hợp đồng pháp lý giữa các bên cam kết không tiết lộ các thông tin độc quyền, bí mật kinh doanh cho bên thứ ba。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Accord de non-divulgation","explanation":"Contrat légal (NDA) par lequel les signataires s'engagent à garder confidentielles les informations stratégiques échangées。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["NDA","Confidentiality Agreement"],
