      ja: {"term":"弱参照","kana":"よわさんしょう","note":"メモリ逼迫時に限らず、GC（ガベージコレクション）実行時に参照先オブジェクトが強制的に回収対象となる参照形式。"},
      zh: {"term":"Java 弱引用","explanation":"Java 中的一种对象引用机制。被弱引用关联的对象只能生存到下一次垃圾回收发生之前，无论当前内存是否足够都会被 GC 回收。"},
      en: {"term":"Java Weak Reference","explanation":"A reference type in Java that does not prevent its referent from being made eligible for garbage collection by the JVM."},
      my: {"term":"Java အားပျော့သော ရည်ညွှန်းချက်","explanation":"JVM ၏ Garbage Collector က ၎င်းရည်ညွှန်းခံရသော object ကို memory မပြည့်မီကတည်းက GC လုပ်တိုင်း ဖျက်ဆီးခွင့်ပြုသည့် အားနည်းသောချိတ်ဆက်မှု。","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Tham chiếu yếu trong Java","explanation":"Loại tham chiếu không ngăn cản đối tượng bị dọn dẹp bởi bộ thu gom rác (garbage collector) trong phiên quét tiếp theo。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Référence faible Java / WeakReference","explanation":"Type de référence (WeakReference) n'empêchant pas son objet d'être collecté par le ramasse-miettes dès le prochain cycle。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["WeakReference"],
      related: ["java_concurrency_utilities"],
      example: {"java":"WeakReference<MyCache> ref = new WeakReference<>(new MyCache());"},
      source: "project-glossary-v2",
      ko: { term: "Java 약한 참조", explanation: "참조 대상 객체가 가비지 컬렉터(GC)에 의해 언제든지 회수될 수 있도록 허용하는 참조 유형으로, 주로 메모리 리스크가 큰 캐시 데이터 관리에 쓰입니다." }
