      zh: {"term":"跨站脚本漏洞防御","explanation":"Web 安全编码手段。主要通过对动态输出到 HTML 页面中的数据进行彻底的字符实体转义（沙箱化处理），以及配置内容安全策略（CSP），简称 XSS 防御。"},
      en: {"term":"Cross-Site Scripting Prevention","explanation":"Defensive coding practices, such as HTML escaping, context-aware output encoding, and Content Security Policy (CSP), to mitigate XSS risks."},
      my: {"term":"XSS ညစ်ညမ်းကုဒ် ကာကွယ်ရေးစနစ်","explanation":"HTML escape ဖြင့် ဝင်လာသော script ကုဒ်များကို သာမန်စာသားအဖြစ် ပြောင်းလဲခြင်းနှင့် CSP နည်းလမ်းဖြင့် XSS တိုက်ခိုက်မှုကို ကာကွယ်ခြင်း。","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Phòng chống tấn công chèn kịch bản chéo trang","explanation":"Kỹ thuật mã hóa ký tự đầu ra (HTML escaping) và áp dụng chính sách bảo mật nội dung (CSP) để vô hiệu hóa mã độc XSS。","needsReview":true},
