      ja: {"term":"HTTPステータスコード (3xx)","kana":"ステータスコードさんびゃくばん","note":"リクエストを完了するために、ブラウザ側で追加の操作（リダイレクトなど）が必要であることを示す応答コード（301、302など）。"},
      zh: {"term":"HTTP 3xx 重定向状态码","explanation":"HTTP 协议响应状态码。表示客户端请求的资源已发生变更，需要采取进一步的重定向操作才能完成，如 301 永久重定向、302 临时重定向。"},
      en: {"term":"HTTP Status Codes 3xx","explanation":"A class of HTTP response status codes indicating that further action (such as redirection) must be taken by the client to complete the request."},
      my: {"term":"HTTP ပြန်လည်ညွှန်းပို့မှုကုဒ် 3xx များ","explanation":"တောင်းဆိုထားသော resource သည် နေရာရွှေ့သွားသဖြင့် browser ဘက်မှ redirect ထပ်လုပ်ရန် လိုကြောင်း ညွှန်ပြသည့်ကုဒ်များ (ဥပမာ- 301)။","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Mã trạng thái HTTP 3xx","explanation":"Nhóm mã phản hồi HTTP yêu cầu trình duyệt khách hàng phải thực hiện chuyển hướng (redirection) để hoàn thành truy cập。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Codes d'état HTTP 3xx / Redirection","explanation":"Catégorie de codes HTTP indiquant au client qu'il doit effectuer une redirection pour accéder à la ressource (ex. 301)。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["HTTP 3xx","HTTP Redirect"],
      related: ["http_status_codes_2xx"],
      example: {"text":"HTTP status codes 3xx tell search engines to update their link index to the new URL."},
      source: "project-glossary-v2",
      ko: { term: "HTTP 상태 코드 3xx", explanation: "클라이언트가 요청한 자원에 대한 추가적인 변경이 있어, 다른 위치로 재접속(리다이렉션)하라는 추가 동작을 브라우저에 지시하는 응답 코드군(301, 302 등)입니다." }
