      zh: {"term":"HTTP 4xx 客户端错误状态码","explanation":"HTTP 协议响应状态码。表示请求包含语法错误或无法被满足，属于客户端自身的错误，如 400 Bad Request、403 Forbidden、404 Not Found。"},
      en: {"term":"HTTP Status Codes 4xx","explanation":"A class of HTTP response status codes representing client-side errors, indicating problems with the request itself."},
      my: {"term":"HTTP တောင်းဆိုမှုအမှားကုဒ် 4xx များ","explanation":"Client ဘက်က တောင်းဆိုမှု မှားယွင်းခြင်း၊ ဝင်ခွင့်မရှိခြင်း သို့မဟုတ် ရှာမတွေ့ခြင်းတို့ကို ပြသည့် အမှားကုဒ်များ (ဥပမာ- 404 Not Found)။","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Mã trạng thái HTTP 4xx","explanation":"Nhóm mã phản hồi báo lỗi từ phía khách hàng (client-side errors), bao gồm cú pháp sai hoặc không có quyền truy cập。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Codes d'état HTTP 4xx / Erreur client","explanation":"Classe de codes HTTP indiquant une anomalie dans la requête du client (ex. 400 Bad Request, 404 Not Found)。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["HTTP 4xx","client error status codes"],
      related: ["http_status_codes_3xx"],
      example: {"text":"A broken link typically returns HTTP status codes 4xx, specifically 404 Not Found."},
      source: "project-glossary-v2",
      ko: { term: "HTTP 상태 코드 4xx", explanation: "클라이언트의 요청 구문 오류, 인증 누락, 혹은 잘못된 자원 이름 요구 등 송신 주체에 문제가 있음을 가리키는 오류 코드군(400, 401, 403, 404 등)입니다." }
